page.title: 20ALPHA & OMEGA
page.content:
{Contributors:} Sarah Alford, Michael Barnes, Terry Gilligan, Jan Hellyer, Christine Hill, Maureen Jepson, Mary Loadman, Ishbel & Andrew Sewell, David Stanley, Jack Watts, Ron & Dorothy Wilkins
{We speak for our community:}some young some old; some lifelong Dabchicks, some neighbours, some newcomers; for those who come from distant parts in Britain and those from overseas: Aust- ralia, France, Germany, Italy, Phill- ipines, Poland, Sweden & USA
We wish you well in 2885: may peace and prosperity, hope, faith and charity abound with you, as we pray it may with us - to you the World rolls forward as it leaves us behind
'Seek and you shall surely find'
